name: MET Ocean Forecast
description:
Ocean forecasts for points at sea in Northwestern Europe.

Delivers wave and sea forecast in standard [MET Forecast GeoJSON](https://docs.api.met.no/doc/ForecastJSON) format. There is also an XML variant, but this is considered legacy and exists only for backwards compatibility.

The forecast is based on multiple wave and sea models. For more information on models and parameters, see [the Oceanforecast data model documentation](https://docs.api.met.no/doc/oceanforecast/datamodel).

When importing this API, please set `https://api.met.no` as URL when prompted.
